<h2>Account Deletion Request</h2>

<p>We're sorry to see you go. If you would like to delete your ReferVo account and all associated data, please follow the instructions below.</p>

<h3>How to Delete Your Account</h3>

<p><strong>Option 1: In-App Deletion</strong></p>
<p>You can delete your account directly in the ReferVo app:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Open the ReferVo app</li>
  <li>Go to <strong>Profile</strong> tab</li>
  <li>Tap <strong>Settings</strong></li>
  <li>Scroll down and tap <strong>Delete Account</strong></li>
  <li>Confirm your decision</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Option 2: Email Request</strong></p>
<p>If you cannot access the app or prefer to request deletion via email, please contact us:</p>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@refervo.com?subject=Account%20Deletion%20Request">support@refervo.com</a></p>
<p>Please include the email address associated with your ReferVo account.</p>

<h3>What Gets Deleted</h3>
<p>When you delete your account, we will permanently remove:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your profile information (name, email, phone number)</li>
  <li>Your business information</li>
  <li>Your connections</li>
  <li>Your in-app messages</li>
  <li>Your referral history</li>
</ul>

<h3>What We May Retain</h3>
<p>Certain information may be retained as required by law or for legitimate business purposes:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Transaction records (for tax and legal compliance)</li>
  <li>Data necessary for fraud prevention</li>
  <li>Information we are legally required to retain</li>
</ul>

<h3>Processing Time</h3>
<p>Account deletion requests are typically processed within 7 business days. You will receive a confirmation email once your account has been deleted.</p>

<h3>Questions?</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about account deletion, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@refervo.com">support@refervo.com</a>.</p>
